A6 greeting card, blank inside for your own message.  Your card is printed on beautiful matt 360g recycled stock, and will come to you with a brown Kraft recycled envelope, packaged in a cello bag to keep it squeaky clean!

For bulk buying options click on drop down menu below.  You can choose ANY mix of cards from the black and white range, please list your choices in the PayPal message box.

Free UK postage.

I also supply wholesale, please contact me for terms and prices.
